body:
Seriously I want to climb and get better at the game. I accept that I have to carry people who are bad and that&#039;s fine I just hate failing to carry those who dont care. Literally every game I lose is people playing ranked but not caring whether they win or lose because of some stupid reason like &quot;I dont want so and so to win&quot; or &quot;It&#039;s just a game I want to have fun&quot;

This shit needs to stay in norms or better yet out of the game all together, nobody has fun going 0/20 and being useless or AFK&#039;ing over some petty dispute. I wish the report and ban system was faster to get some of this cancer out of matchmaking.

I have heard however that this is actually a bigger problem in OCE than any other region and I just pray that either I can carry enough games to get out of this elo or Riot becomes faster in their banning and more thorough.
